sub_title: Medical Doctor with a focus on mental health, health inequities and migration
summary: I am an enthusiastic, ambitious and socially concerned medical doctor. I have a special interest in primary and mental health care. The right to health is a human right, that's why I am comitted to health care for undocumented migrants and refugees.
